              <p>We are a healthcare-focused technology platform dedicated to making healthcare accessible for everyone. MediLocate connects patients with clinics across Canada, providing a simple way to find, book, and manage medical appointments. Our mission is to ensure that every Canadian has access to timely healthcare without the hassle of long wait times and countless phone calls. Our team is composed of dedicated individuals passionate about healthcare and technology, driven to create the most seamless experience for patients and healthcare providers alike.</p>
